{
  "chapter": 64,
  "chapter_summary": "第六十四回 真相白\n\n芮玮在黎昆寿宴上揭露简召舞冒充身份，出示黎小姐定情汗巾，简召舞恼羞成怒点中芮玮麻穴，当众宣称芮玮是简召舞，欲借众人之手除掉他。简召舞偷学黎小姐武功，连出怪招将芮玮击成重伤。钱飞龙暗中救下芮玮，假称其已死，将尸体抛入江中，又潜入江底救起。芮玮苏醒后与钱飞龙相认，易容药被江水溶掉，露出与简召舞相同的容貌。本章揭露简召舞弑母杀弟、杀害叶青夏诗的罪行，展现芮玮为妻妾复仇的决心，以及钱飞龙的义举。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_kun",
      "text": "这是莫家牧场的寿礼，祝贺老寿星长寿百岁，福寿并增。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_fei_long",
      "speaker_name": "钱飞龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这贺礼一定是三手神抓偷的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这贺礼在过江上被一位瘦小的老汉从莫兄身上盗得，在下转手盗来，那位老汉盗得重宝，上岸即走，不知去向，是故众人并没有人见他来过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_kun",
      "text": "黎老英雄请收下这礼物，在下等于帮老英雄寻回重宝，不知凭这点可否请见贤婿婚前一面？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_kun",
      "speaker_name": "黎昆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，去请芮玮出来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_kun",
      "speaker_name": "黎昆",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "贤婿，你可识得此人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_li_kun",
      "text": "不识。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "姓简的，你当真不识我吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "你认不认得我没有关系，在下要请你认一件东西，你不认得我，这件东西想是一定认得！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不错，这汗巾我认得，你从哪里得来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "这汗巾是黎小姐送给你的定情之物吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不错，这汗巾正是黎小姐送给区区的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "简召舞呀！简召舞呀！你若不是为了匆匆赶回参加黎昆的擂台招亲，怎会遗失黎小姐赠送的汗巾，可见天网恢恢，偏叫你遗下汗巾，教我想出凶手是谁！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_niang",
      "text": "娘，你将来不要怪我，你这位儿子我一定要杀，我要报仇，报那血海深仇。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "黎小姐送给你的定情之物，你为什么不好好看着而遗落我家。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你家？你是谁？你住在哪里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "我的儿子呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你的儿子，我怎知你的儿子在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你到底是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "我姓芮……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不用说了，我知道你是谁，你是天池府的大公子简召舞。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_fei_long",
      "speaker_name": "钱飞龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人内脏震碎，已经死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qian_fei_long",
      "text": "真的死了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_kun",
      "speaker_name": "黎昆",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "玮儿，今天是你大喜之日，为何杀人行凶，冲了喜气。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_li_kun",
      "text": "此人是天池府的大公子，他弑母杀弟，小婿早已不忿，今日碰上，不想失手杀死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_kun",
      "speaker_name": "黎昆",
      "listener": "char_bang_zhong",
      "text": "快把尸体抬走，现场收拾干净，不要使贺客看了恶心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qian_fei_long",
      "text": "我……我……才是芮玮……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 64,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    }
  ],
